Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.11,0:01:03.81,CN_interviewee,,0,0,0,,我完全
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:04.81,CN_interviewee,,0,0,0,,我们知道这个中立这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:06.25,CN_interviewee,,0,0,0,,我是完全能够容忍这个
